   <head>Epigrammi - XXXI. Atramentum scriptorium.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1">
     <l n="1">Ferrum putre situ spumanti fervet aceto,</l>
     <l n="2">Mandet ut aeternis scripta voluminibus.</l>
     <l n="3">Scilicet hoc illud, vatum volitare per ora,</l>
     <l n="4">Hoc est, Pyramidas vincere, Nile, tuas.</l>
     <l n="5">Infelix fatum: sanies rubiginis ergo</l>
     <l n="6">Eripit inviso nomina nostra rogo?</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
  </body>
